---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

// Halaman Layanan (ID) - Full 6 Cards
---

<Base title="Layanan IT Infrastructure">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1 class="mb-8 font-bold text-4xl">Layanan Profesional IT</h1>
      <p
        class="mb-12 text-lg text-text-light dark:text-darkmode-text-light max-w-2xl mx-auto"
      >
        Solusi infrastruktur jaringan dan server yang aman, stabil, dan terukur
        untuk mendukung operasional bisnis Anda.
      </p>

      <div class="row justify-center text-left">
        <div class="col-12 mb-8 sm:col-6 lg:col-4">
          <div
            class="card p-8 shadow-md border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border rounded-xl h-full hover:border-primary transition duration-300 bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
          >
            <h3 class="h4 mb-4 font-semibold text-primary text-2xl">
              Network Setup
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
              Konfigurasi Mikrotik, Cisco, Firewall, dan optimasi Bandwidth
              Management untuk koneksi yang stabil.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 mb-8 sm:col-6 lg:col-4">
          <div
            class="card p-8 shadow-md border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border rounded-xl h-full hover:border-primary transition duration-300 bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
          >
            <h3 class="h4 mb-4 font-semibold text-primary text-2xl">
              Server Admin
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
              Instalasi & maintenance Linux/Windows Server, serta implementasi
              Virtualisasi (Proxmox/VMware).
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 mb-8 sm:col-6 lg:col-4">
          <div
            class="card p-8 shadow-md border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border rounded-xl h-full hover:border-primary transition duration-300 bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
          >
            <h3 class="h4 mb-4 font-semibold text-primary text-2xl">
              Cloud & Monitoring
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
              Implementasi Cloud Infrastructure dan sistem monitoring 24/7
              menggunakan Zabbix atau Grafana.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 mb-8 sm:col-6 lg:col-4">
          <div
            class="card p-8 shadow-md border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border rounded-xl h-full hover:border-primary transition duration-300 bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
          >
            <h3 class="h4 mb-4 font-semibold text-primary text-2xl">
              IT Security
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
              Audit keamanan jaringan, manajemen Firewall, proteksi data, hingga
              pembersihan sistem dari malware.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 mb-8 sm:col-6 lg:col-4">
          <div
            class="card p-8 shadow-md border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border rounded-xl h-full hover:border-primary transition duration-300 bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
          >
            <h3 class="h4 mb-4 font-semibold text-primary text-2xl">
              Managed IT
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
              Dukungan teknis On-Demand, pemeliharaan hardware/software rutin,
              dan troubleshooting harian kantor.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 mb-8 sm:col-6 lg:col-4">
          <div
            class="card p-8 shadow-md border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border rounded-xl h-full hover:border-primary transition duration-300 bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
          >
            <h3 class="h4 mb-4 font-semibold text-primary text-2xl">
              Consultancy
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
              Konsultasi strategis perencanaan infrastruktur, audit sistem IT,
              dan solusi teknologi efisien bagi bisnis.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <section class="section pt-0">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="mb-16 text-center">
              <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold">Alur Kerja Saya</h2>
              <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg opacity-80 mb-12">
                Proses kerja yang transparan, terstruktur, dan berorientasi pada
                hasil.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
              <div
                class="mb-6 rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
              >
                <div
                  class="row items-center justify-center text-center md:text-left"
                >
                  <div class="col-12 md:col-2 mb-4 md:mb-0">
                    <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary opacity-30"
                      >01</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-12 md:col-10">
                    <h3 class="h4 mb-2 font-bold">Konsultasi & Audit</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80">
                      Menganalisis kebutuhan bisnis secara mendalam dan
                      melakukan audit menyeluruh pada infrastruktur IT yang
                      sedang berjalan.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div
                class="mb-6 rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
              >
                <div
                  class="row items-center justify-center text-center md:text-left"
                >
                  <div class="col-12 md:col-2 mb-4 md:mb-0">
                    <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary opacity-30"
                      >02</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-12 md:col-10">
                    <h3 class="h4 mb-2 font-bold">Desain & Eksekusi</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80">
                      Merancang blueprint sistem yang efisien dan melakukan
                      instalasi serta konfigurasi perangkat dengan standar
                      profesional.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div
                class="mb-6 rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-darkmode-border p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body"
              >
                <div
                  class="row items-center justify-center text-center md:text-left"
                >
                  <div class="col-12 md:col-2 mb-4 md:mb-0">
                    <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary opacity-30"
                      >03</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-12 md:col-10">
                    <h3 class="h4 mb-2 font-bold">Uji Coba & Serah Terima</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80">
                      Melakukan testing stabilitas sistem secara penuh sebelum
                      diserahterimakan, diikuti dengan dukungan pemeliharaan
                      rutin.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  
  
  </Base
>
